OL,5, A Scottish government minister who ran 
OL,6, up an #11,000 data roaming bill on his 
OL,7, iPad in Morocco had been warned almost 
OL,8, a year earlier to update his device.   
OL,10,FMichael Matheson ran up "huge" charges 
OL,11,Fwhile on holiday last Christmas because
OL,12,Fhis parliament-issued tablet had not   
OL,13,Fbeen switched to a new data provider.  
OL,15,FBBC News understands Mr Matheson was   
OL,16,Ftold via email to swap out the sim card
OL,17,Fin the device in February 2022.        
OL,19,FOpposition MSPs have urged the health  
OL,20,Fsecretary to cover the bill himself.   
